data.description: Don't walk but run! To this beautiful home on 1.2 acres in the charming neighborhood of Misty Harbor. In this split plan home that has been freshly painted you will find hardwood floors in the vast family room. Down the hall you will see a spacious master bedroom with a spectacular bathroom featuring a jacuzzi tub, separate shower, dual vanity and impressive walk in closet. Along the hall near the kitchen you will see 2 bedrooms that share a jack and jill style bathroom. Looking out from the family room outside you'll see an immense backyard. This house is ready for you to call it home. This breathtaking community features a gated entrance, marina, tennis courts, pool and much more. Don't hesitate make your appointment today!!
